            <title>[SOLR-1024] Calling abort on DataImportHandler import commits data</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1024</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If abort is called on an ongoing import, the import is cancelled but the data is committed. It should be rolledback.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
